name: Jason Elder
text: Everyone here is super nice! I wish there was more seats at the bar area but covid has put a stop to that, not their fault. Nora is so nice and even though I can't see her smiling because of the mask, she is always very polite and kind! Laura is super awesome! She is very polite and makes me feel welcome!

name: Benita Kutsche
text: Consistent pizza at all locations. Staff here was very nice. However there is limited seating, not enough table for large parties.

name: Madhuri Mehta
text: We went there on Sunday. It was clean and wasn‚Äôt crowded at all. I liked the ceiling decor at this place. We ordered bruschetta and veg out pizza. The order came on time and it was hot. The pizza was delicious however I found bruschetta a bit on sour side cuz of its sauce. Rest of the experience was good.

name: Kendra Simmons
text: I love that Mellow Mushroom has vegan cheese.  The one I recently went to here in Georgia had the follow your heart vegan cheese.  You can get a vegan pizza or a vegan calzone or sub sandwich. Lots of veg friendly items.

name: John Saari
text: Picked up a pizza and an order of hummus.  Was able to make an online order requesting mushrooms on one half of the pie. The order was correct and the pizza was delicious as usual.  The hummus was also very good. This is one of my 2 go to places for great pizza and their crust is exceptional.  My order was ready for pickup on time.

name: Willie Kelly
text: Lovely service, and great food.  Interesting flavors presented beautifully. Always my favorite!

name: Phil McCarroll
text: Healthy as pizza can be. Use whole wheat dough and fresh veggies.

name: Michael Jones
text: Wings were good and pizzas had plenty of toppings. Parking left a lot to be desired. Employees were friendly.

text: The service was extremely poor. The people that work behind the counter give zero effort in trying to provide good service.

If you are looking for an extensive menu , an awesome atmosphere,  unsurpassed service and delicious food, you can't beat this place!!
